340
00:19:11,590 --> 00:19:12,660
Setelah saya berpuas hati,

341
00:19:13,590 --> 00:19:14,810
Saya sendiri akan menuntut nyawanya.

342
00:19:31,680 --> 00:19:32,680
Puan Ye.

343
00:19:35,200 --> 00:19:37,020
