428
00:24:07,440 --> 00:24:08,326
Di mana gadis Soulshift

429
00:24:08,350 --> 00:24:09,550
Saya bawa balik beberapa hari lepas?

430
00:24:10,070 --> 00:24:11,900
Dia masih dikurung.

431
00:24:12,680 --> 00:24:14,290
Minta Tuan Han bawa dia kepada saya.

432
00:24:26,070 --> 00:24:27,070
Tingyan.

433
00:24:27,200 --> 00:24:28,200
Tingyan.

434
00:24:43,070 --> 00:24:45,220
Adakah ia menyakitkan, Tingyan?

435
00:24:47,790 --> 00:24:48,790
