539
00:31:48,680 --> 00:31:50,980
Tidak, Guru Besar.

540
00:31:52,040 --> 00:31:53,040
Tolong jangan.

541
00:31:53,150 --> 00:31:54,150
Tidak.

542
00:32:01,070 --> 00:32:03,770
Chuhui!

543
00:32:04,240 --> 00:32:06,460
Tahan diri anda, Puan Yue.

544
00:32:07,110 --> 00:32:09,290
Bukankah anda berkata anda boleh menyelamatkannya,

545
00:32:10,240 --> 00:32:12,180
adakah anda

546
