Tatasusunan hampir lengkap.

582
00:34:47,880 --> 00:34:50,610
Sima Jiao, nombor anda sudah habis.

583
00:34:51,190 --> 00:34:52,190
Sima Jiao.

584
00:34:55,840 --> 00:34:56,840
Sima Jiao.

585
00:34:59,670 --> 00:35:01,310
Inilah saat yang saya tunggu-tunggu.

586
00:35:22,040 --> 00:35:23,040
Bagaimana ini boleh berlaku?

587
00:35:26,710 --> 00:35:29,500
Bolehkah seseorang dalam
Lapan Istana telah membantunya?

588
00:35:31,750 --> 00:35:32,750
Chuhui.

589
00:35:34,070 --> 00:35:35,070
Chuhui!

590
00:35:49,590 --> 00:35:50,590
Puan Ye.

591
00:35:52,040 --> 00:35:54,210
Saya nampak awak bercakap

592
00:35:54,520 --> 00:35:55,840
