593
00:35:56,400 --> 00:35:57,520
Apa yang awak cakapkan?

594
00:35:59,040 --> 00:36:01,040
Mereka cuba memujuk saya
supaya tidak melayan Sima Jiao,

595
00:36:01,320 --> 00:36:02,320
tetapi saya menolak.

596
00:36:04,040 --> 00:36:06,050
Adakah anda mengesyaki saya, Guru Sekte Shi?

597
00:36:08,630 --> 00:36:11,420
Anda dan Liao Tingyan

598
00:36:11,840 --> 00:36:12,980
