653
00:39:59,320 --> 00:40:01,250
Hentikan, Memerintah.

654
00:40:02,440 --> 00:40:04,570
Keputusan, jika anda berterusan,

655
00:40:05,550 --> 00:40:07,130
macam mana kita masih boleh berkawan?

656
00:40:09,190 --> 00:40:10,730
Adakah anda sendiri juga?

657
00:40:11,040 --> 00:40:12,166
Adakah anda juga seorang pemalas,

658
00:40:12,190 --> 00:40:13,530
