663
00:40:27,230 --> 00:40:28,730
Adakah semua hari yang kita kongsi

664
00:40:29,360 --> 00:40:30,360
akan berakhir di sini?

665
00:40:30,670 --> 00:40:31,670
ya.

666
00:40:35,590 --> 00:40:39,020
Mata awak berkilauan.

667
00:40:41,920 --> 00:40:42,920
