675
00:41:03,840 --> 00:41:05,690
Jika saya memanggil anda dengan ini...

676
00:41:05,880 --> 00:41:07,126
Jika awak perlukan saya,

677
00:41:07,150 --> 00:41:08,730
Saya akan muncul di sisi awak bila-bila masa.

678
00:41:25,440 --> 00:41:25,980
Cepat.

679
00:41:26,440 --> 00:41:27,440
Bergeraklah.

680
00:41:30,710 --> 00:41:32,690
Kenapa awak baring? bangun.

681
00:41:34,110 --> 00:41:35,420
Hei, bergerak lebih cepat.

682
00:41:37,360 --> 00:41:40,860
Kini, Puak Sima hanya tinggal Sima Jiao.

683
